# CODEOWNERS for Conceptus Veritas Backend Repository
# ---------------------------------------------
# This file defines code ownership for the Conceptus Veritas backend repository.
# Code owners are automatically requested for review when someone opens a pull 
# request that modifies code they own. Multiple owners can be specified.
# Order is important - the last matching pattern takes precedence.

##########################################
# TEAMS AND RESPONSIBILITY AREAS
##########################################

# Team Definitions (for reference):
# @conceptus-veritas/backend-leads - Lead backend developers responsible for architecture and core functionality
# @conceptus-veritas/backend-developers - All backend developers
# @conceptus-veritas/security-team - Security specialists
# @conceptus-veritas/devops - DevOps and infrastructure specialists
# @conceptus-veritas/database - Database specialists
# @conceptus-veritas/ai-team - AI and ML specialists
# @conceptus-veritas/docs - Documentation specialists
# @conceptus-veritas/api-team - API design specialists

